#10302
seifer figure~
Seifer~
A young figure in a trench coat is leaning on his gunblade.
~
This Paladin knows no remorse. As the proclaimed SorceresS' Knight, he
will do anything to defend her honour, even if it means his very death.
But with wielding "Lionheart", the Legendary Gunblade - he will be a 
match for anyone.
~
