#10301
sorceress zeal~
The SorceresS~
A young woman, although very tired on her throne, awaits your presence.
~
The Ruler of Trabia Garden, proclaimed by the false prophets to free the world
from the very chaos of everyday life, is Zeal Roniji - The SorceresS.
Nothing much is known of her past, althought it was rumored that she was the
Evil Queen which had craved for the destruction of this world.
As you ponder on this, she raise her head and look at you with stunning blue
eyes. Looking at her, you are amazed at the beauty of her long flowing hair,
the softness of her white, tender skin and the sheer intelligence of her
powerful mind which is affecting you all now.

'You have come in vain dear mortal', she suddenly say as if she was reading
your heart... her voice, is like sweet music to your ears.
~
