#10307
Zylara girl~
Zylara~
A beautiful teenager lies here playing with her german shepard.
~
This beautiful, long blond hair girl... Daughter of the Divine SorceresS,
the Crystal Child is here standing ablazed in all of her glory. Dressed
from head to toe in sparkling jewelry with soft makeup, you blush as
you take a step backwards, afraid to smear her beauty with your unworthy
presence. Suddenly, a growl brings you back to the present as a Huge
German Shephard rushes into the room and snuggle against her lap.

'Eh? Heh heh puppie,' Zylara says sweetly as she smiles at you.
~
