#10308
Jia figure~
Jia~
A hooded figure is here contemplating you softly.
~
One of the only surviving Jedi Masters from the Apocalypse, this beautiful
young woman lost all hope of a peaceful life. Being hunted down by the
Ramous Siths for years, she has finetune her skills to a point where the
Force is a living part of her soul. Now, with the coming of the proclaimed
SorceresS in this despised world, she now see a glimmer of hope and will
do whatever it takes to achieve it...
~
